     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame>. Vediamo come:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Prendiamo un vettore <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object67" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.25in" svg:height="0.2917in"><draw:object>
