   <text:p text:style-name="Standard" loext:marker-style-name="T2">le grandezze <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">+</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">-</text:span> e <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">+</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">-</text:span> sono, rispettivamente, le ampiezze di probabilità di trovare <text:span text:style-name="T2">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">0</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">=+k </text:span>ed<text:span text:style-name="T2"> m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">0</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">=-k </text:span>quando il sistema si trova negli stati <text:span text:style-name="T2">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">=+k </text:span>e <text:s text:c="3"/><text:span text:style-name="T2">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">=-k.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5">Ma quanto vale l’ampiezza di probabilità di trovare <text:span text:style-name="T2">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">=+k </text:span>misurando <text:span text:style-name="T2">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span> su atomi che si trovano nello stato <text:span text:style-name="T2">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">=+k</text:span>?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5">L’ampiezza di probabilità cercata è pari al prodotto</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P5"><text:tab/><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object100" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="1.5165in" svg:height="0.35in"><draw:object>
