      </draw:frame>Il modulo quadrato di ognuno di questi numeri complessi, ad esempio <text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">k</text:span>, da la probabilità che misurando la grandezza <text:span text:style-name="T2">g</text:span> esca il particolare valore <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object159" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.2252in" svg:height="0.2665in"><draw:object>
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
         <semantics>
          <mrow>
           <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
            <msub>
             <mover accent="true">
              <mi>g</mi>
              <mo stretchy="false">¯</mo>
             </mover>
             <mstyle mathsize="8pt">
              <mi>k</mi>
             </mstyle>
            </msub>
           </mstyle>
           <mrow/>
          </mrow>
          <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ { bar  {g}} rSub { size 8{k} } } {}</annotation>
         </semantics>
        </math>
       </draw:object><draw:image>
        <office:binary-data>VkNMTVRGAQAxAAAAAAAAAAEAGwAAAAkAAAAAAAAAAAABAAAAAQAAAAEAAAABAAAAAfoAAABA
         AQAAHQAAAJYAAQACAAAACQCLAAEAAgAAAP//gQABABAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAPkAAAA/AQAAiwAB
         AAIAAAAAGJUAAQAEAAAAAAAAAJYAAQACAAAACQCLAAEAAgAAAB8AigABAEIAAAAFADwAAAAK
         AE9wZW5TeW1ib2wAAAAAAADwAAAA//8AAAAABQAAAAAAAAD/AwAAAAAAAAABAP8DAAAAAAAA
         AAAAAACIAAEAAgAAAAEAhwABAAUAAAD/////AIYAAQAEAAAAAAAAAHIAAgAaAAAABwAAAOcA
         AAABAAAArwB4AAAAAAABAAEArwCMAAEAAAAAAIsAAQACAAAAHwCKAAEASAAAAAUAQgAAABAA
         TGliZXJhdGlvbiBTZXJpZgAAAAAAAPAAAAAAAAAAAAAFAAAAAAACAP8DAAAAAAAAAAEA/wMA
         AAAAAAAAAAAAAIgAAQACAAAAAQCHAAEABQAAAP////8AhgABAAQAAAAAAAAAcgACABcAAAAM
         AAAA1wAAAAEAZ3gAAAAAAAEAAQBnAIwAAQAAAAAAiwABAAIAAAAfAIoAAQBIAAAABQBCAAAA
         EABMaWJlcmF0aW9uIFNlcmlmAAAAAAAAoAAAAAAAAAAAAAUAAAAAAAIA/wMAAAAAAAAAAQD/
         AwAAAAAAAAAAAAAAiAABAAIAAAABAIcAAQAFAAAA/////wCGAAEABAAAAAAAAAByAAIAFwAA
         AI4AAAAeAQAAAQBrRwAAAAAAAQABAGsAjAABAAAAAACMAAEAAAAAAIwAAQAAAAAA
        </office:binary-data>
       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame><text:s/>associato al numero considerato.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P9">In generale se il sistema si trova in uno stato <text:span text:style-name="T7"></text:span> e si misura una grandezza <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr3" draw:name="Object160" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.2252in" svg:height="0.2665in"><draw:object>
